Package com.anthem.selenium.utils

This package consists of all Utility classes that can be used for enhanced functionality.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ATAFFileUtils
    This class provides methods for handling file operations.
    CommonUtils
    This class provides Common Utility methods.
    DatabaseUtils
    This class provides the methods for handling basic database functionality.
    To use the methods from this Utility, make sure to have required JDBC Driver jar file in class path.
    DateTimeUtils
    This class provides Utility methods of Date and Time functionalities.
    ExcelUtils
    This class consists of generic methods to handle Excel based operations.
    FTPUtils
    This class consists of generic methods to handle FTP Operations only.
    HTMLTableUtils  
    ReadWordDocxUtils
    This class provides methods for reading content from an MS Word document (.docx format only).
    RESTWebServiceUtils
    This class provides the methods for Consuming and querying REST Webservices.
    SOAPServiceUtils
    This class provides the methods for Consuming and querying SOAP Webservices.
    XMLJSONUtils
    This class provides the methods for handling JSON and XML Objects.
